# Project Images Directory

Place project images here. Images will be served at:
http://localhost:3001/images/projects/[filename]

Image naming convention:
- project-id_1.jpg (primary image)
- project-id_2.jpg
- project-id_3.jpg
etc.

Supported formats: .jpg, .jpeg, .png, .gif, .webp
Recommended size: Max 1920x1080, optimized for web
